H epilogh gia to pou tha mpei to pod ginete mesw labels dld

NODE
kubectl label nodes <node-name> <label_key>=<label-value>
kubectl label nodes node01 size=Large

POD
kai mesa sto pod
modeSelector:
  size: Large


  -----------------------------------------------------------
  hte meso Affinity

NODE
  kubectl label nodes <node-name> <label_key>=<label-value>
    kubectl label nodes node01 size=Large
    

POD
  apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: example-pod
spec:
  containers:
  - name: nginx
    image: nginx
  affinity:
    nodeAffinity:
      requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
        nodeSelectorTerms:
        - matchExpressions:
          - key: size
            operator: NotIn
            values:
            - Small




            affinity:
            nodeAffinity:
              requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
                nodeSelectorTerms:
                - matchExpressions:
                  - key: color
                    operator: In
                    values:
                    - blue



            spec:
            containers:
            - name: nginx
              image: nginx:1.14.2
              ports:
              - containerPort: 80
            affinity:
              nodeAffinity:
                requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
                  nodeSelectorTerms:
                  - matchExpressions:
                    - key: size
                      operator: Exists



Psaxnei na vrei to pod kata to execution kai an den to vrei den sinexiszei alla an ginei h alagh to pod sinexizei na doulevei etsi mexri na termatistei         
requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution

Psaxnei na vrei to pod kata to execution kai an den to vrei to vazei opou nane alla an ginei h alagh to pod sinexizei na doulevei etsi mexri na termatistei         
preferedDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution

Psaxnei na vrei to pod kata to execution kai an den to vrei den sinexiszei alla an ginei h alagh to pod sinexizei na doulevei me tis kainouries alages kai kanei restart         
requiredDuringSchedulingrequiredDuringExecution